<section class="reviews" id="reviews">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>What guests<br /><em>are saying</em>.</h2>
      <p>From wedding receptions to weekend food truck runs — here's what the Metro East is saying about Chef B.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"Chef B catered my daughter's wedding and the food was absolutely incredible. The whole-pig roast was the highlight of the night. Guests are still talking about it months later."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <span class="reviewer-name">Tanya M.</span>
          <span class="reviewer-event">Wedding Reception · O'Fallon, IL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"We booked Chef B for our corporate holiday party — 80 guests, full buffet. The mac &amp; cheese alone had everyone going back for thirds. Flawless from setup to cleanup."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <span class="reviewer-name">Marcus D.</span>
          <span class="reviewer-event">Corporate Event · Belleville, IL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-quote">"The Jerk Pork Mac from Doggie Macs is something special. I drive from St. Louis every time the truck is open. Nothing else like it in the region."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <span class="reviewer-name">Keisha R.</span>
          <span class="reviewer-event">Doggie Macs Regular · St. Louis, MO</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
